# RealSmart suite

Eight Herd apps share design language, Flux Pro UI, RealSmart shell, and Google-first login.

| App | Path |
|-----|------|
| zebidee | `~/Herd/zebidee` |
| staff-dash | `~/Herd/staff-dash` |
| smaps | `~/Herd/smaps` |
| smartbadges | `~/Herd/smartbadges` |
| smartcops | `~/Herd/smartcops` |
| sos2 | `~/Herd/sos2` |
| plan2do | `~/Herd/plan2do` |
| smartdocs | `~/Herd/smartdocs` |

**Auth:** Per-app sessions (not SSO). Google via Socialite + fwd.host. See `smartbadges/docs/auth.md`.

**sars** (`~/Herd/sars`) is separate — no suite switcher.
